channel.title: About switching to dedicated server host
channel.description: I am planning on switching to a dedicated server host. VPS can't handle 140+ people, it starts lagging bad after a while. I temporary host my server in my computer but the server still lags a bit when it hits 170+ people online. So I am planning to get a dedicated host. Does anyone know a good dedicated host that would not lag with 200+ people online? The ones that you actually used and performed great.
